Package: hpolcc
Type: Package
Title: Hierarchical air pollution model
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Patrick Brown
Maintainer: Patrick Brown <patrick.borgnine@gmail.com>
Description: A package for hierarchical functional case crossover models. This package provides tools for modeling air pollution health effects with hierarchical structures and case crossover designs.
